HEADWORD: Significator
<hw>Sig"ni*fi*ca`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>significateur</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who, or that which,
signifies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In this diagram there was one <qex>significator</qex> which
pressed remarkably upon our astrologer's attention.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W.
Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Significatory</ent>⟦br⟧
